<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Jokes Catalog</title>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="header-container">
    <div class="logo">
      <%= image_tag 'logo.png', alt: 'Site Logo', width: '150' %>
    </div>
    <h1>Welcome to Jokes Catalog!</h1>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="content">
  <h2>Your daily dose of laughter!</h2>
  <p>Looking for a quick laugh? You've come to the right place! <br>
    Jokes Catalog is a collection of the funniest jokes from around the web. <br>
    Whether you like puns, one-liners, or classic jokes, we've got something for everyone.</p>

  <div class="cat-image">
    <%= image_tag 'laughing-cat.jpg', alt: 'Laughing Cat', width: '400' %>
  </div>

  <div class="no-center">
    <h2>What's inside?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Puns:</strong> Get ready for the best wordplay!</li>
      <li><strong>Dad Jokes:</strong> So bad they're good.</li>
      <li><strong>Knock-Knock Jokes:</strong> Because who's there?</li>
      <li><strong>Random Fun:</strong> A mix of jokes that will surprise you!</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p>Feel free to explore, laugh, and share your favorite jokes with friends!</p>
  <br>
  <a href="/jokes" class="cta-button">Browse Jokes Now</a>
  <br>
</div>

<footer>
  <p>&copy; 2024 Jokes Catalog. All Rights Reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
